Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.12,0:21:11.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.26,0:21:13.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴迪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.03,0:21:17.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是这么笨手笨脚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.53,0:21:20.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明就是依古西奥拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.52,0:21:26.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}finally I lost the world
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.03,0:21:26.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那塔鲁？
